                <h1>Athena Goddess: Wisdom & Warfare in Greek Mythology</h1>
                <p>Athena, the Greek goddess of wisdom and warfare, symbolizes intellect and strategy. Born from Zeus's head, she embodies strength and rationality, guiding heroes like Odysseus. Revered as the protector of cities, especially Athens, her wisdom inspires civic responsibility and cultural achievements, making her one of mythology's most respected deities.</p>
